{"chunk": "Tax on profit or loss for the year represents 22% of the
book profit or loss adjusted for non-taxable and non-
deductible items.
Skat af årets resultat udgør 22 % af det regnskabsmæssige
resultat korrigeret for ikke indkomstskattepligtige og ikke
fradragsberettigede poster.
Skat af årets resultat er sammensat af den forventede skat", "context": "The chunk provides details on the calculation of tax on the company's profit or loss for the year, including the applicable tax rate and adjustments for non-taxable and non-deductible items. This information is part of the company's accounting policies disclosed in the notes to the financial statements."}
